text: Anu diggah Yallal kelta, usuk yi Rabbiiy sin Rabbi kinniih usuk kullim yamlikeeh kay amri maleh tu yoo maxagtaay usuk kulliimih qamal geyto le Rabbi kinni, toysa rooci eelli haytaamay baax√¥ bagul mutuccu itta matan Yalli tet yamlikeeh amol teetik yan kaa akke waytek, diggah yi Rabbik madqaay mekla cakki gital takkeeh, meqem abte num maqaanel galtaah umam abte num umaanel galta keenik iyye
